channel.title: "Washed Out" (made with Auxy) played on RinseFM!
channel.description:
Excited that one of the first tunes I made in Auxy almost a year ago got played on the illustrious RinseFM over the weekend!
Here's a radio rip: https://soundcloud.com/secretagentgel/washed-out-furious-styles-rinse-rip
Check out the full version here: https://soundcloud.com/secretagentgel/washed-out
I just had to brag! Couldn't have done it without Auxy!
